OL,3,CInside the 'pleasant' school offering
OL,4,Cits teachers fortnightly days off
OL,6,FWords by a teacher at West Grantham
OL,7,FSecondary Academy
OL,9,FI've worked at WGSA since 2020, for
OL,10,Fthe first 3 years I commuted from
OL,11,FLeeds to Grantham and eventually moved
OL,12,Fcloser to school. The school have
OL,13,Falways been very supportive and take
OL,14,Ftime to listen to staff views on
OL,15,Fwellbeing.
OL,17,FLast academic year the school gave me
OL,18,Fa 1pm finish on a Friday so I could
OL,19,Fcollect my children from school every
OL,20,Fweek and avoid the Friday A1 traffic.
