OL,3,CInside the 'pleasant' school offering
OL,4,Cits teachers fortnightly days off
OL,6,FThe school runs an electric car scheme
OL,7,Fto help employees with travel which
OL,8,Fwas very useful to me when traveling
OL,9,F800 miles a week.
OL,11,FStaff work load is thought about by
OL,12,Fmanagement and marking policies
OL,13,Freflect that, which gives the staff
OL,14,Fmore time to prepare for teaching than
OL,15,Fendless marking.
OL,17,FThis year I've trialled the flexi-day
OL,18,Fscheme, this runs over a 2 week cycle
OL,19,Fand enables me to have a Friday off
OL,20,Fevery other week.
