OL,3,CInside the 'pleasant' school offering
OL,4,Cits teachers fortnightly days off
OL,6,FIt's been really good, it's giving me
OL,7,Fa chance to catch up on things I
OL,8,Fusually wouldn't be able to do
OL,9,Fthroughout the week, like going out on
OL,10,Fmy bike, picking up my kids from
OL,11,Fschool.
OL,13,FIt's brilliant to look forward to a
OL,14,Fthree day weekend every 2 weeks. It
OL,15,Fallows me to catch up on work if
OL,16,Fneeded or just enjoy a day doing what
OL,17,FI like.
OL,19,FI've worked in a number of schools and
OL,20,Fthis by far the most pleasant one to
OL,21,Fwork in.
